The paper deals with deep multi-task learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and genomics tasks, which are all subfields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of stochastic algorithms, which is a common technique in neural networks and optimization (cs.NE).
